                        <title xml:lang="en">Commentary on the books of Exodus and Deuteronomy.</title>
                        
                        
                        
                        <note>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Fragments of an anonymous Arabic commentary on Exodus and Deuteronomy, comprising Ex. 8-12, 14-20, and Deut. 16-21.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>The anonymous writer refers to his own commentaries on the Pentateuch as well as to several other authorities.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </note>
                     
                     
                     
