                           <collation>
                              
                              
                              
                              <p>The quires divided into 2 parts: 18 quires of 10 leaves each (folios 1-159, nos. 8-14, 19-27, 31-32) and 7 quires of 10 leaves each (folios 160-205, nos. 4-5, 8-9, 11, 13-14). </p>
                              
                              
                              
                              <p>Quires nos. 8, 9, 19, 22, 25, 26, 27, 31 of the 1st part, and nos. 4, 5, 8, 9, 13 of the 2nd part are defective.</p>
                              
                              
                              
                              <p>Signatures in Arabic letters on the first page of a quire, and with Arabic letters on the first page of the four following folios.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           </collation>
                           
                           
                           
                           <condition>
                              
                              
                              
